section.def:
Hong
        Kong ship
        (香港船舶) means a ship registered in Hong Kong;

loader
        (裝載人) means the person undertaking the loading of grain
      in bulk into a ship;

paragraph.content:
all free grain surfaces in partly filled cargo space shall be trimmed level
                    and secured in accordance with A16, A17 or A18 of the Grain
                    Code;
